description:
StorReduce is pioneering a virtualization layer containing numerous unique technologies for companies to move data to and better use it at scale on object storage and cloud. StorReduce's vision is to enable enterprises to have a single cloud data lake with no data silos, that is affordable, scalable and maximizes the data’s business value.

One technology in the StorReduce virtualization layer is software defined, scale-out deduplication with a cloud native interface. The only deduplication built for modern cloud object storage, StorReduce reduces object storage costs, speeds up transfer, by up to 97% and enables reuse of the data and metadata on object storage with generic cloud services. (See StorReduce Malware Detection demo at https://youtu.be/9_FNSqaNUDU.)
A single StorReduce cluster can handle 10s to 100s of petabytes of data at extremely high throughputs and enables new business cases such as removing backup appliances and storing primary backups straight to object storage or cloud.
 
Other technologies in the StorReduce layer include: Object Clone, Deduplicated Replication, StorReduce Insight and more. See storreduce.com for details.
 
StorReduce was 1 of 4 partners worldwide for the AWS S3 Infrequent Access launch, 1 of 8 partners worldwide for the Google Cloud Coldline launch and was recommended by Gartner as a cloud deduplication software in their report: Market Guide for Data Center Backup Targets.
 
StorReduce is in production around the globe and is recommended by most leading clouds and private object stores.

StorReduce software installs on-premises or in your cloud or object store in minutes and is available for Free Trial by contacting StorReduce.
    640 West California Avenue, Suite 210, Sunnyvale, CA 94086, US

Our philosophy:


We don't aim to be the biggest recruitment consultancy but we do aim to be the best. We help businesses build  powerful teams that deliver against exceptionally high standards by holding ourselves up to those same values. Quality and integrity are our watchwords and we like to think we're different. Here's a flavour of why:

• We have specialist recruitment teams who are experts in their area. Whether they're recruiting in accountancy, HR or legal, you won't find them working outside their area of expertise
• Our consultants don't work on commission, but instead rely on team work to ensure the right person is placed in the right job
• We will never send out your CV without express permission. Quite simply, we don't think it's right

We're proud of what we've achieved so far. But we don't look back, we're always innovating:

• We were the first recruitment consultancy to launch a recruitment outsourcing business

Suvola is a cybersecurity company creating solutions for the three major shortcomings of current information technology systems in use today.  These three major shortcomings are in the areas of identity, tampering, and authentication and are responsible for the vast majority of cybercrime.

Identity management and protection of user credentials has been one of the biggest challenges in cybersecurity.  To address this, Suvola has developed the ambient identity device.  This advanced piece of identity technology can be embedded in everyday wearables and equipment to provide either primary or secondary verification of the identity of the user or equipment without the need for user names, passwords, PIN codes or other forms of user entry information based validation.  The Suvola ambient identity device complies with all industry standards  for identity and authentication devices and uses BLE technology for communications.  By using ambient identity devices, users can have a far more secure and trusted environment while also experiencing a far more convenient way of managing their identity online.

To address tampering, Suvola is creating a secure and trusted software platform to support a line of cloud infrastructure, web services and enterprise data management software for the enterprise information technology appliance market. Packaged and sold as self-contained rack-mountable devices for cloud or enterprise infrastructure, the Suvola tamper-proof computing platform addresses the need for more cost-effective, easier to manage information technology infrastructure to support tablet, mobile and the emerging Internet of Things applications with advanced security and trust.
tagLine: Advancing the science of cybersecurity by creating products and services that make cyberspace safer for all of us

description:
Access simple and elegant -- but POWERFUL -- solutions for the most significant challenges of Internet Marketing

As youʼve probably noticed, marketing is rapidly moving online.

Sure, traditional marketing (print, TV, radio) isnʼt going to totally disappear, but itʼs quickly getting displaced by online marketing. For example:
• The vast majority of people now search for a local business online rather than use the Yellow Pages
• Most people now comparison shop online before making almost any purchase
• Almost one in ten people on the planet are active users of one of the social networks
• Every industry has a competitor thatʼs “crushing it” by using the Internet as their dominant means of marketing

This shift of marketing from offline to online is so recent and happening so fast that most businesses are struggling to keep up (or, worse, still trying to get started) -- especially given the growing complexity of what it takes to be successful.

For example, Internet Marketing used to mean just having a website - but, no longer. Now, it also requires the use of email autoresponders, social networking, online video/ audio, article distribution and much more.

The reality is that most business people have little interest in learning about this stuff -- but the Internet technologists donʼt seem to understand that. They continue to make totally unrealistic assumptions about what a businesses person can do, wants to do or has time to do with online marketing.

description:
Wenn „Digitalisierung“ auf Unternehmen trifft, zieht das nicht nur einen technologischen Wandel nach sich. Es bewirkt vor allem massive Veränderungen im Arbeitsalltag der einzelnen Mitarbeiter und im Zusammenspiel der Gesamtorganisation. contexxt.ai bereitet Organisationen und Mitarbeiter auf diese Veränderungen vor, begleitet sie hindurch und macht die Entwicklung messbar – mit datengestützter Analyse und methodischem Beratungsvorgehen.

Unternehmen jeder Größenordnung stehen vor der unvermeidbaren Herausforderung, Arbeitsprozesse und Arbeitsplätze zu digitalisieren. New Work, Workplace 4.0 führen zu Veränderungen in den Arbeitsweisen, vor allem aber auch in der Zusammenarbeit. Diese Veränderungen haben große Potenziale, bringen aber auch entscheidende Herausforderungen mit sich – die Mitarbeiter müssen wollen, sonst sind alle Vorhaben von Anfang an zum Scheitern verurteilt.

Unsere Coachingmandate helfen, die Digitalisierungsvorhaben strukturiert und zielgerichtet im Unternehmen zum Erfolg zu bringen. Klarer Fokus dabei ist es, messbare und belegbare Ergebnisse zu erzielen. Effiziente Workshopformate, etablierte und praxiserprobte Vorgehensweisen und nicht zuletzt effiziente Analysen und datengetriebene Erfolgsmessungen führen transparent zu schrittweisen Ergebnissen.

contexxt.ai hat es sich zur Aufgabe gemacht, den Nutzen von Technologien für den einzelnen Menschen in den Vordergrund zu stellen – um Motivation und Sinnhaftigkeit zu erhöhen und um die Eigenschaften, die Menschsein ausmachen, mehr in den Vordergrund der Arbeit zu stellen: Kreativität und Emotionalität. Denn für den Digitalisierungsprozess müssen unternehmensindividuelle Handlungsfelder und nutzenorientierte Lösungen definiert werden, die nicht nur an den Unternehmenszielen, sondern vor allem am Bedarf der Mitarbeiter sowie an der Unternehmenskultur ausgerichtet sind – nur so werden durch neue Arbeitsformen positive Effekte erzielt…
tagLine: Wir bringen die Nutzenaspekte neuer Technologien in die Köpfe der Menschen.

COQOS Hypervisor SDK supports a large bundle of features corresponding to the virtualization standard VIRTIO, creating maximum flexibility: guest operating systems can be used and reused on different Systems on Chips. OpenSynergy cooperates with the primary Operating System (OS) providers to ensure that Android, AGL, AliOS, and other OS are entirely supported.

COQOS Micro SDK is the virtualization variant for microcontrollers, mainly used in the safety-critical real-time domain. Typical application domains are powertrain, chassis, body, gateway, and ADAS control units, which implies the separation kernel must achieve a high safety level of ASIL-D. 
The automotive leading Bluetooth® stack Blue SDK is one of OpenSynergy's communications platforms. It is the reference Bluetooth® implementation for many OEMs around the world. The variant Blue SDK Fusion offers a reliable Automotive-Grade Bluetooth stack for Android™ Automotive OS. 

OpenSynergy further provides complimentary Automotive-Grade software components tailored for the Android Open Source Project (AOSP) to boost Android's adoption in the automotive domain.

OpenSynergy also provides engineering services to support the customization of its products.
Read more on www.opensynergy.com
tagLine: OpenSynergy provides embedded software products for the next generation of vehicles.

A TOPCHAMPS é uma plataforma de RH que faz a gestão de OKRs, avaliação de desempenho e remuneração estratégica.

1) Gestão de OKRs:
A metodologia de OKRs ou "Objetivos e Resultados Chaves"​ foi criada pela Intel, adotada pelo Google, Samsung, Disney, Microsoft, etc. Em função de sua eficiência muitas empresas no Brasil vem a aderindo metodologia que serve para eliminar a subjetividade das metas de cada cargo, atribuindo métricas numéricas (indicadores) para o alcance do objetivo. A plataforma permite um cascateamento dos indicadores da empresa e sua estratificação entre os departamentos e colaboradores. Também através da plataforma é possível fazer o acompanhamento dos indicadores da empresa, departamentos e colaboradores de maneira a facilitar a atuação dos gestores sobre os indicadores que estiverem abaixo da meta.

2) Avaliações de Desempenho:
As avaliações de desempenho levam em consideração 2 aspectos:
- Quantitativos: Expressos pelo alcance dos indicadores (vs metas) da empresa, departamentos e/ou colaboradores.
- Qualitativos: Expressos pela aderência dos colaboradores às competências do cargo.

O gestor de RH estabelece a periodicidade dessas avaliações e define o peso dos aspectos quantitativos e qualitativos assim como de cada indicador e competência. O gestor responsável pela avaliação poderá dar feedbacks através da plataforma para corrigir a conduta de sua equipe e melhorar esses indicadores e aderência às competências.

3) Remuneração Estratégica:

Por fim, as avaliações de desempenho podem ou não, estar atreladas à remuneração do colaborador. A meritocracia costuma gerar resultados impactantes na produtividade da empresa. A plataforma tem a opção de apresentar o bônus/PLR e comissões em tempo real que podem estar condicionadas ao alcance dos indicadores da empresa, departamentos e/ou colaboradores.

A Topchamps promove a integração dos interesses de empregados e empregadores, para que todos sonhem juntos numa mesma direção.

www.topchamps.com. 

    Rua Joaquim Silva, 11 SL.907 - Glória,  Rio de Janeiro, Rio de Janeiro 20241-110, BR
tagLine: Gestão de OKRs, avaliação de desempenho e remuneração meritocrática
siegeSocial: Rio de Janeiro, Rio de Janeiro

Edusity crosses barriers and borders bringing teachers and students on to the same platform, no matter where in the world they might be. It is a real-time, online learning platform that allows the classes to be conducted online using patent-pending technology which removes the notion that teaching can only be done in closed classrooms. It has all the features and tools a teacher would need in today’s teaching methodology to run an engaging classroom, including interactive whiteboard, audio and video support, active student participation, direct and group interaction, directed and taught coursework options, examinations and testing options, grading and much more. Edusity is the only true online learning platform that allows for an active participation from the parents by allowing them to check how their child is doing in the classroom real-time and monitor their progress. Unlike the number of DIY (Do-it-yourself) platforms available, Edusity brings the closed classroom environment online through real-time teaching.

Edusity is available on a SaaS model where teachers can sign up and put their courses online, use our exclusive technology platform and take in a lion’s share of their course fees. In this model, we bring the students to the teachers and promote their courses through our unique online branding initiatives. We think these companies are, in a strange way, a tough fit for the existing financial players: too capital efficient for venture capital, too small for private equity and too messy for strategics. Wir sind eine 2017 gegründete Hamburger Technologie-Firma, die sich ganz der Digitalisierung von betrieblichen Arbeitsprozessen verschrieben hat. Die Software die wir entwickeln ist schlank, modern, sicher und auf die echten Bedürfnisse von Unternehmen angepasst.
￼
Unsere Expertise im B2B-Bereich entstammt der langjährigen Erfahrung in der Entwicklung von cloud-basierten ERP-Systemen und branchenübergreifenden SaaS Software-Tools. Es ist dem täglichen Umgang mit den Geschäftsprozessen unserer Kunden zu verdanken, dass wir ein klares Bild davon besitzen, worauf es bei der Digitalisierung wirklich ankommt.

￼
Für uns stellt die Dienst- und Schichtplanung einen Kernaspekt mittelständischer Unternehmen dar, bei dem noch wesentliches Verbesserungspotential vorhanden ist. Unser Ziel ist es daher, Unternehmen, die noch auf Basis einer händischen bzw. Excel-basierten Arbeitsweise ihre Dienstplanung vornehmen, eine kostengünstige digitale Alternative an die Hand zu geben, die sich mühelos in den betrieblichen Alltag integrieren lässt. Wir möchten Mittelständlern und Startups außerdem dabei helfen, von teuren – und meist auch unnötig komplizierten – Softwareangeboten abzusehen und stattdessen auf kostengünstige und moderne Cloud-Anwendungen wie Aplano umzusteigen.
Unsere Vision ist, dass sich Kunden mit Hilfe unserer Software wieder auf das wesentliche im Betrieb konzentrieren können – ohne sich mit den lästigen bürokratischen Aspekten des Arbeitsalltags herumschlagen zu müssen. Apano ist eines unserer Produkte, mit dem unsere Kunden schon heute dieses Ziel verwirklichen.

We’ve created Homeis because we know first hand how deep the experience of being foreign-born is. When you ask us what home is, we don’t have an easy answer. It’s complicated. We have the city we chose to live in and call home, and then we have our culture, the country we come from, which we call home as well. And it’s a big part of our identity, it’s who we are.

Homeis was created to help people like us, who belong here and there, and feel that the Internet is undeserving them. We’ve witnessed how difficult it is for local foreign-born communities to digitally connect, share their culture, their local knowledge, and unique context. We saw how important these communities are in one’s life, how supportive they can be, and how effective their common wisdom can be to its members.

So we decided it’s time to give foreign-born communities a dedicated comprehensive product. A product that understands them really well, and most importantly - empowers them. It’s what we’re here for. While local culture networks have always existed, our mission is to use technology and innovation to turn these invisible groups into visible communities.

Homeis was founded in Feb 2017 in NYC and Tel Aviv. We’ve launched our first community in Dec 2017. We currently have Indian, Israeli, French, African and Mexican communities- and many more to come! As most foreign-born people, we are BIG dreamers. Join us!
